SELECT sum(e * f), max(f) FROM v GROUP BY mod(e, 5)
----
Explained Query
  Project (#1, #2) // { arity: 2 }
    Reduce group_by=[(#0 % 5)] aggregates=[sum((#0 * #1)), max(#1)] // { arity: 3 }
      Get materialize.public.v // { arity: 2 }

Source materialize.public.v
  Demand (#0, #1)

